     ‚Ėď                                Notes:                              ‚Ėą


     ‚Ėą  You paid your dues in THUG. Now prove yourself in THUG 2. You've 
     ‚Ėą  been chosen by Tony Hawk to take on Bam Margera as your teams go
     ‚Ėą  on a World Destruction Tour. It's time to go globetrotting on an 
     ‚Ėą  insane road trip. THUG 2 grinds in with a hilarious story mode, 
     ‚Ėą  an unprecedented level of customization, and more moves than the
     ‚Ėą  Skate Gods could dream of. Grab your board, an arsenal of 
     ‚Ėą  spray-paint... jump into the tour van and wreak havoc across the
     ‚Ėą  globe.
