     ‚Ėď                            Game Features:                          ‚Ėą


     ‚Ėą  ‚Ėļ World Destruction Tour: Hawk recruits YOU onto his team for a 
     ‚Ėą    no rules, no limits world tour versus Bam Margera. You invade 
     ‚Ėą    international cities and wreak havoc, proving yourself to the
     ‚Ėą    pros as you live the ultimate skateboard adventure. 
     ‚Ėą
     ‚Ėą  ‚Ėļ All New Team Play: Team Hawk versus Team Bam. Play as yourself
     ‚Ėą     or switch to play one of your teammates or a special guest 
     ‚Ėą    skater - over 20 unique characters. 
     ‚Ėą
     ‚Ėą  ‚Ėļ Unparalleled Customization: Create your own logo for use in 
     ‚Ėą    graffiti tags, skate stickers with the all new 
     ‚Ėą    'Create-A-Graphic' feature. Familiar Hawk customization 
     ‚Ėą    continues with 'Create-A-Goal,' 'Create-A-Park' and the 
     ‚Ėą    revolutionary 'Face In The Game' feature. More Player Control 
     ‚Ėą    Than Ever Before: Tear it up with sticker slaps, projectiles,
     ‚Ėą    crazy vehicles, hilarious tantrums, and slow-motion Focus
     ‚Ėą    Control. 
     ‚Ėą
     ‚Ėą  ‚Ėļ 2 Games In 1: Team up and wreak havoc in Story Mode or switch
     ‚Ėą    and play 15 levels in Classic Mode. Complete your all-time 
     ‚Ėą    favorite goals like S-K-A-T-E, Secret Tape, and High Score 
     ‚Ėą    against a 2-minute timer.
